{"type":"message","id":"5bc8f77b","parentId":"d2032dd7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:12:37.019Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_eds8me8kztg8_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 2549\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=920\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 031218 - The TIC experiment requires implementing a classifier to distinguish invariant vs variant content across pulse logs. I need to examine existing pulse logs and create the initial implementation.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"fast-wharf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 2549\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=920\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 031218 - The TIC experiment requires implementing a classifier to distinguish invariant vs variant content across pulse logs. I need to examine existing pulse logs and create the initial implementation.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774336357018}}
